title: How to Paint: Da Red Gobbo's Surprise in 10 paints
description:
Da Red Gobbo loves stealing presents, and cramming them into his massive Lootbag. But this year, someone has already been pinching his gifts! In this Warhammer guide, we’ll be painting the mischievous Red Gobbo in 10 paints, so you can start the Grot Revolushun before the da big boss finds out and ‘krumps him good’. 
       
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
